James Bianco Urges Defensive Investing (Audio)

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-30T16:35:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/james-bianco-urges-defensive-investing-audio-.html
James Bianco, president of Bianco 
Research LLC in Chicago, says investors should move to a 
"defensive position" since there is a "better than fifty 
percent" chance the U.S. is in recession. Bianco talks with 
Bloomberg's Ken Prewitt and Tom Keene on Bloomberg Radio's 
"Bloomberg Surveillance."     (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 10:10
 